entity.saltwatermobs.lacedon.name=Lacedon
entity.saltwatermobs.lacedon.description=Deadly aquatic creatures that induce the weight effect which usually drags their victim down to the bottom of the ocean. They are able to come onto land for a small amount of time and indefinitely if it is raining.
achievement.lacedon.kill=Codswallup!
achievement.lacedon.kill.desc=Slay a Lacedon.
achievement.lacedon.learn=Sea Men!
achievement.lacedon.learn.desc=Add a Lacedon to your Beastiary.
achievement.lacedon.summon=Fishtastic!
achievement.lacedon.summon.desc=Summon a Lacedon.
entity.saltwatermobs.skylus.name=Skylus
entity.saltwatermobs.skylus.description=Squid like creatures that form and live in tough shells. If damaged enough, their shells will break, this reduces their defense but increases their attack and movement speeds. Their attacks blind with ink.
achievement.skylus.kill=Shell Smasher!
achievement.skylus.kill.desc=Slay a Skylus.
achievement.skylus.learn=Coming Out The Shell!
achievement.skylus.learn.desc=Add a Skylus to your Beastiary.
achievement.skylus.summon=My Magic Aquarium!
achievement.skylus.summon.desc=Summon a Skylus.
entity.saltwatermobs.ika.name=Ika
entity.saltwatermobs.ika.description=Slow snail-turtle-shellfish! Ika can be lured and bred with vegetables, however they can only survive on land for a small amount of time. Farm with care!
achievement.ika.kill=Rock Pool Bully!
achievement.ika.kill.desc=Slay an Ika.
achievement.ika.learn=Sea Farming!
achievement.ika.learn.desc=Add an Ika to your Beastiary.
entity.saltwatermobs.abtu.name=Abtu
entity.saltwatermobs.abtu.description=Vicious fish with big teeth! It is rare to find adults, but if you do, you best swim away as they will swarm you with their children!
achievement.abtu.kill=Fish Slapped!
achievement.abtu.kill.desc=Slay an Abtu.
achievement.abtu.learn=The Biting Wont Stop!
achievement.abtu.learn.desc=Add an Abtu to your Beastiary.
entity.saltwatermobs.raiko.name=Raiko
entity.saltwatermobs.raiko.description=Large sea birds known to dive into the ocean and snatch their prey to fly up high and drop their their prey back into the ocean with the weight effect, eventually drowning their prey.
achievement.raiko.kill=Power Diving!
achievement.raiko.kill.desc=Slay a Raiko.
achievement.raiko.learn=Evil Pelicans!
achievement.raiko.learn.desc=Add a Raiko to your Beastiary.
achievement.raiko.tame=Sky Fishing!
achievement.raiko.tame.desc=Tame a Raiko.
entity.saltwatermobs.roa.name=Roa
entity.saltwatermobs.roa.description=Ferocious shark like beasts that dominate the sea! Roas create deadly whirlpools around them to pull their prey towards their deadly jaws! The brave or foolish attempt to tame them as mounts.
achievement.roa.kill=Whirlpools?!
achievement.roa.kill.desc=Slay a Roa.
achievement.roa.learn=Jaws!
achievement.roa.learn.desc=Add a Roa to your Beastiary.
achievement.roa.tame=Sea King!
achievement.roa.tame.desc=Tame a Roa.
entity.saltwatermobs.herma.name=Herma
entity.saltwatermobs.herma.description=Giant crabs! They usually keep to themselves unless something gets too close!
achievement.herma.kill=Crabby!
achievement.herma.kill.desc=Slay a Herma.
achievement.herma.learn=Cokey Cokey!
achievement.herma.learn.desc=Add a Herma to your Beastiary.
achievement.herma.tame=Battle Crab!
achievement.herma.tame.desc=Tame a Herma.
entity.saltwatermobs.quetzodracl.name=Quetzodracl
entity.saltwatermobs.quetzodracl.description=Powerful flying pterosaur wyverns with a strong grasp!
achievement.quetzodracl.kill=Pterosaur Dragons!
achievement.quetzodracl.kill.desc=Slay a Quetzodracl.
achievement.quetzodracl.learn=Pterosaurs Aren't Dinosaurs BTW!
achievement.quetzodracl.learn.desc=Add a Quetzodracl to your Beastiary.
achievement.quetzodracl.tame=Rend The Skies!
achievement.quetzodracl.tame.desc=Tame a Quetzodracl.
